ENAITURUK

Ore empalai e dukuya e PETERO naa ilairukok apa etisirakaki ooipotoki tene aajo “Iltung'ana oogeluno le Nkai”, ooidapashakinote apa moikuape e Asia. Ore enkipirta ena palai naa pee eitagol ilaisumak oota apa enyamali kitok tenkaraki enkirukoto enye. Ore olasirani neitodolu ena eitadamu ilaisumak ilomon supati le Yesu Kristo, laa te nkeeya enye, o empiunoto enye, o enkisiligata e lotunoto enye naisho ninche osiligi. Ore tenkaraki nena baa neishiaakino neng'amaa nengiri osina lenye, eyiolo meeta olng'ash aajo entemata natemi enkitashoto e nkirukoto enye, naa kelaakini ninche teina “olong neibalunyeki Yesu Kristo.”

Ore ake sii teina kitagoloto oo nkoishuaa tenkata enyamali, etasayiaka olasirani ilaisumak peyie etoni te nkop anaa iltung'ana oora ile Kristo.

